name: Cave Diver (markuzo)
description:
CAVE DIVER 

  • Goal: explore the caves, get the pearl and resurface before the time runs out. Watch out for obstacles!
  • Movement: WASD/ZQSD/Arrows - Space/Return to use.
  • Special keys: ] (no damage) - [ (reveal map)

Fait pour VIDEO GAMES LAB: Game Jam 2021 pendant le week-end 6-7 Novembre  | Created for VIDEO GAMES LAB: Game Jam 2021 during the weekend 6-7 November.
